snippet.title: Chiyo-chan no Kagi [ちよちゃんの鍵] Game Sample - PC/Doujin
snippet.description: Another "Solomon's Key" doujin title along with games like "Princess Lana" and "Memories of Solomon's Key", except featuring Azumanga Daioh characters and a funny opening and ending which is a spoof/parody of "South Park" (called East Park in reference to the land of the rising sun). It was developed by Sygnas, who have developed popular doujin titles like Imas Champ. While I had cuter thumbs I could select, I chose the SP parody one (I can always get cute thumbs). Enjoy.
